same client code with a proxy:&quot;) proxy = Proxy(real_subject) client_code(proxy) # output: # Client: Executing the client code with a real subject: # RealSubject: Handling request. # Client: Executing the same client code with a proxy: # Proxy: Checking access prior to firing a real request. # RealSubject: Handling request. # Proxy: Logging the time of request.

